Linux driver for Cypress FX2 USB peripherial controller

To build the driver, you need blackfin toolchain, avaiable on AnalogDevices homepage.

Set up enviroment variable PATH:
export PATH=~/blackfin-sources/build/bfin-elf/bin:~/blackfin-sources/build/bfin-uclinux/bin:~/blackfin-sources/build/bfin-linux-uclibc/bin:${PATH}

Build with:
make CROSS_COMPILE=bfin-uclinux- ARCH=blackfin